description: Beautiful custom renovated 3+ bedroom/2 bath single family home on four levels in highly desirable Thomas Park neighborhood. Entrance hall leads to front office or den which flows to generous rear living room, both with gas fireplace. Downstairs is a wide open chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances and oversized dining area. Door leads out to lovely patio and garden. Bath with shower on this level as well. Upstairs are two spacious bedrooms and full tile bath. The penthouse level is configured as wide open space with plenty of room for a multitude of uses. The A-frame lines of the eaves create a charming feel in both the full office area with built-in desk as well as in the additional guest room space that adds yet another dimension to this attractive offering. Great closet space, custom lighting and original wide plank pine floors throughout. This lovely home is enviably tucked away on a charming side street and a quick walk to many restaurants, stores and the beach!
